text:
🏋️Fitness Corner, Saujana Rd is located near the Saujana Rd entrance to the Pang Sua Pond.
🧗The exercise equipments were anchored onto a sandpit acting as a natural demarcation.
🏃Joggers may begin or end their exercise regime warming up with some strength training or cool down after their run around the pond.
🧎The convinently located Fitness Corner is accessible to anyone leaving no excuses not to get active.
